overview:
Clicks Internet Marketing, based in Pittsburgh, PA, is an Internet Marketing and Search Engine Optimization (SEO) company focused on growing sales and generating online traffic for businesses and nonprofit organizations.

Our online marketing strategies have a proven track record of increasing sales revenue and getting clients listed higher in organic search results through quality web marketing and strategic planning.

Clicks Internet Marketing provides affordable search engine optimization, pay-per-click advertising services, social media services, and web design and development for our clients.
